The '''''Courane''''' was a [[DP20 gunship/Legends|DP20 gunship]] in service to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] in [[9 ABY/Legends|9 ABY]]. It was part of a small fleet of [[Warship/Legends|warships]] hastily assembled by [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] to defend the [[Meridian sector/Legends|Meridian sector]] from invasion.

